{"tid":1702032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪印張藍卡就可以扮狗","createTime":"2019-11-09T13:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T16:58:58.000Z","uid":69128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac83e0af5edd0db1084599b317c3dbc0c49b4081","tid":1702032,"uid":69128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:17:57.000Z","msg":"「行動呼號」新藍卡曝光　不附晶片必須正面展示 (20:15)<br />\n2019/11/9<br />\n<br />\n警方早前公布，處理示威行動的警員要佩戴「行動呼號」白色卡片作內部識別，據悉警方周三起會將「白卡」轉為「藍卡」，並要求前線警員必須佩戴，不得反轉，高層要求嚴格執行；而佩戴「藍卡」的警員，膊頭編號可除去。但網上流傳「藍卡」將附有晶片，有警官澄清，「藍卡」為一張卡紙，不會附有晶片。<br />\n<br />\n本報上周日記錄集會及衝突地點一帶執勤的防暴警察展示「白卡」情况：319名警員中，合共逾半警員佩戴白卡。惟佩戴率於衝突爆發前後有明顯差別：衝突前，72%警員有佩戴白卡、28%沒有；爆發衝突後有逾六成警員沒展示白卡。警方上周回應傳媒查詢時指出，期望本月內全面推行「行動呼號」優化機制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191109/s00001/1573300749791/「行動呼號」新藍卡曝光-不附晶片必須正面展示\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191109%2Fs00001%2F1573300749791%2F%E3%80%8C%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%91%BC%E8%99%9F%E3%80%8D%E6%96%B0%E8%97%8D%E5%8D%A1%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E4%B8%8D%E9%99%84%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=32f6953c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191109%2Fs00001%2F1573300749791%2F%E3%80%8C%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%91%BC%E8%99%9F%E3%80%8D%E6%96%B0%E8%97%8D%E5%8D%A1%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E4%B8%8D%E9%99%84%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA&h=58fc42d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191109/s00001/1573300749791/「行動呼號」新藍卡曝光-不附晶片必須正面展示</a>"},{"pid":"7d60e258cc9fc21b867ffba9105366106b6c4a40","tid":1702032,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"[集中討論] 為周梓樂同學討回公道<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702027</a>"},{"pid":"ae32aabc587113da8a9847ae76411fe9515e0c11","tid":1702032,"uid":264158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"舊時老人家輪籌睇症咁款"},{"pid":"fa5fb5ba2f6d7e712ca7da03c79900393aab2817","tid":1702032,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45wpEqc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45wpEqc.png&h=efd0aff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oamGHe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oamGHe.jpg&h=e374f630&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}